## 6. Complete Production Pattern

Here is how all three concepts combine in a real product:

```
+------------------+     Queue      +------------------+
|  sensor_task     | ------------> |  process_task    |
|  Priority 5      |  sensor_data_t |  Priority 5      |
|  Reads DHT22     |               |  Formats data    |
|  Every 2s        |               |  Updates display |
+------------------+               +--------+---------+
                                            |
                                     Mutex  | (shared UART)
                                            |
                                   +--------+---------+
                                   |  log_task        |
                                   |  Priority 3      |
                                   |  Logs to serial  |
                                   +------------------+
```

![](images/5.png)

```c
/* Full pattern — app_main */
void app_main(void)
{
    /* Create communication primitives FIRST */
    sensor_queue = xQueueCreate(10, sizeof(sensor_data_t));
    uart_mutex   = xSemaphoreCreateMutex();

    /* Then create tasks */
    xTaskCreate(sensor_task,  "sensor",  4096, NULL, 5, NULL);
    xTaskCreate(process_task, "process", 4096, NULL, 5, NULL);
    xTaskCreate(log_task,     "log",     2048, NULL, 3, NULL);

    /* app_main returns — FreeRTOS scheduler takes over */
}
```

