| Concept          | What it is                 | PC Equivalent     | Use when                   |
| ---------------- | -------------------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------- |
| Task             | Independent unit of work   | Program / process | Always                     |
| Priority         | Who runs first             | Process priority  | Always                     |
| vTaskDelay       | Sleep without blocking CPU | Thread.sleep()    | Always                     |
| Queue            | Thread-safe data pipe      | Email inbox       | Passing data between tasks |
| Binary semaphore | One-shot signal            | Doorbell          | Signalling events          |
| Mutex            | Exclusive resource lock    | Bathroom key      | Shared peripherals         |
